title: SPY's Happy Hour—February 7th, 2014—with mmx and Dr. Edith Eger - Part Two
description: Dr. Edith Eger graces SPY's Happy Hour with her wisdom as she shares her powerful story of growing up as a Jew in Nazi-occupied Eastern Europe. Her extraordinary perspective on the ability to discard limiting beliefs, along with her positive outlook on adversity, has allowed Dr. Eger to view crises as an opportunity for personal growth- and to impart this notion to others' lives.
